20 of this article; and
21 (ii) $100.00 for each plug–in electric drive vehicle that is not a
22 zero–emission vehicle; and
23 (2) After June 30, 2025, at a rate based on the amounts established under
24 item (1) of this subsection adjusted for inflation as determined annually by the
